README file

MC Code Copier Reloaded is a Python program that can capture codes in Anarchia.GG Minecraft Server (OneBlock).

How this works:
Every 30 minutes (while writing this) server is sending some random 10-characters long code (like LrQ9ihPNlq). First player who was the fastest in re-writing this code is receiving 3 AFK keys.

How my program helps:
Program is instantly scanning Minecraft's latest.log file and looking for chat messages. If it recognizes the message template ("Przepisz kod <code here> aby otrzymać nagrodę!"), it will react to it. Then, program is waiting for reward info to appear ("Gracz <player nick here> jako pierwszy przepisał kod w czasie <re-write time> i otrzymał(a) 3 Klucze AFK!"). If it appears, it can save this info. Then it is continuing scanning